# RC Team (Mini IVD)

**Competition:** Mini Innovative Vehicle Design (Mini IVD)
**Vehicle type:** Radio-controlled car (Traxxas-based)

---

## What This Team Does

The RC team designs, builds, and programs a radio-controlled vehicle to meet the Mini IVD challenge parameters. Each year has a new set of requirements around speed, maneuverability, and obstacle tasks.

